<IMG SRC="closet.jpg" HSPACE=10 VSPACE=10 align = left><H2>The Closet </H2>

Though this looks like a closet, it's really the "intern punishment room" for those unruly interns who talk too much or take a long lunch.  Just kidding!  (or are we?)<p>
<br>
