http://www.conservative.org:80/heritage/p_review/fall95/thhim.html 204.71.237.88 19970208221422 text/html 17377
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 22:15:04 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 17-Nov-95 16:29:25 GMT
