&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;<b>William D. Eggers</b> and <b>John O'Leary</b> offer <a href="/heritage/p_review/fall95/thegg.html">community-policing techniques</a> that deter 
crime....<b>John J. DiIulio Jr.</b> explains the <a href="/heritage/p_review/fall95/thiuli.html">real 
causes</a> of falling rates of violent-crime....Alternatives exist to meet the legal needs of the poor after the 
<a href="/heritage/p_review/fall95/thflah.html">abolition of the Legal Services Corp</a>.....Michigan's 
<a href="/heritage/p_review/fall95/thsher.html">welfare reform</a> threatens the effectiveness of faith-
based charities that receive government funding.
<p>
