<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/townhall/hall_of_fame/kirk/kirk1.html 204.71.237.88 19970209111115 text/html 29588
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 11:11:57 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Apr-96 16:40:38 GMT
